Peter_Dawson_(bass-baritone)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair's coach\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"PDCC\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"Athens Olympics gold medallist\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"the team pursuit\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"their first days\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"the club's E\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"grade\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"A-grade races\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"17s\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawson said the duo had worked \\\"three times harder\\\" training at a regional club to get to where they were today than other athletes hailing from cities where cycling facilities were more accessible.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.357316028076095e-16, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the duo\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"three times harder\\\" training\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"a regional club\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling facilities\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They did not have the opportunities of the other clubs in Perth where they can just go to the velodrome and train three or four days a week,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1