mbers helped them to get training rides in and up toPerthfor velodrome practice.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their junior days\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"a community effort\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"the club's members\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"training rides\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"velodrome practice\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you want to make the opportunities for that (velodrome training) to happen, then you have to jump on the train, and you have to miss school,\\\" Dawson said.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.357316028076095e-16, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunities\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"that (velodrome training\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"the train\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It becomes a community; there is two or three parents, and there is other people inside the club that have gone out training with the guys because they need people to train with.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a community\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"two or three parents\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that's kind of how it all comes about.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of getting the guys progressing through, it's been a bit of a club effort.\\\"\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2433}, {\"ngram\": \"a club effort\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing their schooling - Leahy at Mandurah Catholic College and Bleddyn at Frederick Irwin Anglican School and then Applecross Senior High School, during which they trained at the Peel Regional Academy of Sport - both relocated to Adelaide to train at the South Australian Sports Institute.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2497, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandurah\", \"score\": 0.9999999999668034, \"rank\": 3.322402129361652e-11, \"text\": \"Mandurah\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandurah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandurah\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.8843046597711306, \"rank\": 0.11904740865908618, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2527, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bleddyn_ap_Cynfyn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bleddyn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bleddyn_ap_Cynfyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bleddyn_ap_Cynfyn\"}, {\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_in_South_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"South Australian Sports Institute